cb107602915e"],

Cell["\<\
We can also make an interactive version of the ray diagram, by wrapping these \
functions in a Dynamic Module.
Notice we also specify the control elements at specific heights to match the \
electro-optical components\[CloseCurlyQuote] axial positions.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.981449273258204*^9, 3.981449334992324*^9}, {
  3.981449689309497*^9, 
